entries.title: Capture the Star Kimogila
entries.arrival_phase_1: Your targeted entourage will arrive at any moment.
entries.arrival_phase_2: The Star Kimogila has arrived. Disable the vessel and eliminate her escorts!
entries.capture_phase_1: Boarding party is facing light resistance.
entries.capture_phase_2: Resistance eliminated. We've taken the bridge. We'll be underway shortly.
entries.target_disabled: pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < 00ff00 The Star Kimogila has been disabled. Capture operation will begin shortly. pcontrast3 >
entries.capture_started: pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < 00ff00 Primary mission target capture operation underway. pcontrast3 >
entries.capture_complete: pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < 00ff00 Primary mission target capture operation complete! pcontrast3 >
entries.recovery_success: The Star Kimogila has been secured. Good job, pilot.
entries.complete: We've made it to safety. Jumping to lightspeed...now.
entries.failed_escape: The Star Kimogila has escaped the area. This is a disgrace! Return to base at once!
entries.failed_destroy: The Star Kimogila was destroyed! This is unacceptable! Return to base at once. You are to blame for this failure!
entries.abort: Abort code recognized. Stand by for course change... ... Confirmed. You are authorized to leave the system.
entries.escort_wiped_out: pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < 00ff00 The targeted vessel's escort has been eliminated. pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_remaining: pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < 00ff00 %DI ships remain in the vessel's escort. pcontrast3 >
